{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_31094.jpg","bgm":"bgm05_event07","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":830100,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":830100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Gilles de Rais","textRight":"Welcome, esteemed guests.@This is a top-quality Hypocras.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Hypocras...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":400,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"Ah, it's a type of alcoholic drink!@We can't drink it!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"I'm sorry, but...do you have any goat milk or@something?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":830100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Gilles de Rais","textRight":"Ah, right! My Saint is not fond of alcohol!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":830100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Gilles de Rais","textRight":"I'll get what you want right away."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"P-please..."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":830100,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":830100}],"nameRight":"Gilles de Rais","textRight":"...It's truly lamentable.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":830100}],"nameRight":"Gilles de Rais","textRight":"Those soldiers who once@fought alongside La Pucelle,"},{"chara":[{"id":830100}],"nameRight":"Gilles de Rais","textRight":"and witnessed her miracles..."},{"chara":[{"id":830100}],"nameRight":"Gilles de Rais","textRight":"Now, they act as if"},{"chara":[{"id